Title: An Act to Change the Name of Dr. Sixto Antonio Elementary School Unit I in Barangay Bambang, Municipality of Pasig, Metro Manila, to Bambang Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 708
An Act to Change the Name of Dr. Sixto Antonio Elementary School Unit I in Barangay Bambang, Municipality of Pasig, Metro Manila, to Bambang Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Dr. Sixto Antonio Elementary School Unit I in Barangay Bambang, Pasig, Metro Manila, is hereby changed to Bambang Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
